title: Crude suicide rate in Vietnam 2000 to 2015
summary: Overall Crude suicide rate per 100,000 inhabitants has increased over the Year.
Crude suicide rate per 100,000 inhabitants is slightly increasing from 2005 to 2010.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2005 and 2010.
Maximum Crude suicide rate per 100,000 inhabitants, about 7.1 was reported at Year 2010
Minimum Crude suicide rate per 100,000 inhabitants about 6.5 was reached at Year 2005
